main.dc:11: atomic_load allows MemoryOrder Relaxed(0), Acquire(1), or SeqCst(4); got 3
main.dc:15: atomic_store allows MemoryOrder Relaxed(0), Release(2), or SeqCst(4); got 1
main.dc:19: atomic_store allows MemoryOrder Relaxed(0), Release(2), or SeqCst(4); got 3
